dc_description_s: This line shapefile depicts the major rivers in Kenya. These data were created by the U.S. National Imagery and Mapping Agency in 1997. This layer was used throughout multiple maps in "Natures Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being."This data was used in maps featured in Natures Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being.
